{"tid":206862,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好想喺精神病院渡過餘生","createTime":"2017-04-18T15:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T16:59:52.000Z","uid":59569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb54b8b8916d39c487e7d2b255581b658a412253","tid":206862,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:14:25.000Z","msg":"咁我做咩都可以合理<br />\n<br />\n細細個就覺得有另一個自己咁<br />\n屋企有張我唔戴眼鏡既相<br />\n但我睇黎睇去都覺得個個人唔係我自己黎<br />\n一種好陌生既感覺<br />\n<br />\n好鐘意收埋自己<br />\n成日哩埋喺張床度玩手指玩筆<br />\n直到中三個年<br />\n好似唔受控制咁一個人喺公園坐<br />\n個陣明明同緊一個女同學傾計<br />\n後尾我返到屋企再繼續同佢傾個陣<br />\n佢話我做乜變左另一個人咁<br />\n<br />\n其實都幾恐怖下<br />\n又唔可以話係二重人格<br />\n因為我仲有意識<br />\n至少係我腦入面仲會有印象咁<br />\n<br />\n想知有冇其他人同我一樣<br />\n有時會變左另一個人咁<br />\n或者所謂既黑化之類"},{"pid":"b9a5dd9002319795189f080ca1a22da6d0162c14","tid":206862,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:17:37.000Z","msg":"精神病院好多基佬"},{"pid":"4352b16e39553b39191318623a36182335dddbeb","tid":206862,"uid":42170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:18:37.000Z","msg":"睇左醫生先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53d02d91b85780ce9be520f4e6cdb9b46643556","tid":206862,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:19:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>精神病院好多基佬</blockquote><br />\n連登夠多喇"},{"pid":"c19db42c31df926e6affec326c05a8f1d621d65a","tid":206862,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:19:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇左醫生先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔太鐘意睇醫生<br />\n就算我病都係喺屋企自己吽幾日就得"},{"pid":"33426530699ed8b67dbaec2fc673585cc8d3e6a3","tid":206862,"uid":66683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:24:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97d7bd2a3bc50c5f68f4ebec2bfac00c0000d93d","tid":206862,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T15:28:28.000Z","